      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a broad torque curve and 320 hp. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry for superior cornering poise. Significantly, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the Rear Main Seal (RMS) is dry. The exterior shows minor road-going patina but maintains excellent structural integrity, while the interior leather and switchgear remain functional and well-preserved. This is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car ready for the canyons.",
